OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy with rain likely in the west
OL,7,Fand across high ground, more settled
OL,8,Fand drier in the east with a few
OL,9,Fbreaks in the cloud. The wind
OL,10,Fgradually eases over the course of the
OL,11,Fnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy for much of
OL,14,Fthe day with spells of rain at times,
OL,15,Fmostly affecting western hills with
OL,16,Fsomewhat drier conditions further
OL,17,Feast. Temperatures gradually
OL,18,Fincreasing and becoming warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
