OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fand Tuesday, cloudy with spells of
OL,7,Frain at times and remaining a little
OL,8,Fbreezy. Drier and sunnier by
OL,9,FWednesday. Feeling warm or hot by
OL,10,Fthen, with light wind.
